OL,6,FDuring her time in the role, she
OL,7,Fintroduced practices which were
OL,8,Funfamiliar to some living in the
OL,9,Fisland, including keeping
OL,10,Fprescriptions under lock and key
OL,11,Frather than allowing people to collect
OL,12,Fthem unattended.
OL,14,FFollowing some complaints, Sark's
OL,15,FMedical Committee raised concerns with
OL,16,Fthe NHS who investigated Dr
OL,17,FBorchardt's conduct but decided no
OL,18,Faction was needed.
