OL,6,FDr Borchardt also claimed her evidence
OL,7,Fwas not properly considered during the
OL,8,Fprocess and the publishing of the
OL,9,Freport as a Resolution Notice had
OL,10,Fcaused "irreparable harm" to her
OL,11,Fprofessional reputation.
OL,13,FThe judge ruled that Dr Rabey had no
OL,14,Fright to issue a mark against Dr
OL,15,FBorchardt's name because the
OL,16,Finvestigation had not been correctly
OL,17,Fhandled.
