OL,3,C'It's been hell': Doctor wins legal
OL,4,Cbattle over 'flawed' work report
OL,6,FSpeaking about the ordeal, Dr
OL,7,FBorchardt said: "This has come at
OL,8,Fgreat cost financially and personally,
OL,9,Fthe last 18 months has been hell.
OL,11,F"I had a right to defend myself
OL,12,Fagainst all the allegations made
OL,13,Fagainst me, and they didn't allow me
OL,14,Fthat."
OL,16,FReflecting on the judge's verdict, Dr
OL,17,FRabey said: "As Responsible Officer
OL,18,Ffor the Bailiwick, I have a duty to
OL,19,Fprotect patients and the public if
OL,20,Fconcerns are raised about a doctor's
OL,21,Fperformance.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/11
