OL,3,C'It's been hell': Doctor wins legal
OL,4,Cbattle over 'flawed' work report
OL,6,F"This is what I sought to do in this
OL,7,Fcase and I welcome the court's
OL,8,Fjudgment that I was right to
OL,9,Finvestigate the concerns that had been
OL,10,Fraised.
OL,12,F"The judgment also confirmed that I
OL,13,Ffairly considered the system in which
OL,14,Fthe doctor worked in Sark.
OL,16,F"However, the judge also found that
OL,17,Fthere were procedural issues with the
OL,18,Fprocess.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/11
