OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F387A1740763986
OL,3,C'It's been hell': Doctor wins legal
OL,4,Cbattle over 'flawed' work report
OL,6,F"In particular, the judge ruled that I
OL,7,Fshould have picked up that the
OL,8,Findependent investigator I
OL,9,Fcommissioned had not interviewed the
OL,10,Fdoctor last and therefore the process
OL,11,Fof producing the report was flawed.
OL,13,F"In view of the doctor having left
OL,14,FSark in the first half of 2024, I
OL,15,Fdon't intend to re-open the
OL,16,Finvestigation now."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/11
