OL,6,FJason Moriarty, Chief Operating
OL,7,FOfficer for the States of Guernsey,
OL,8,Fadded: "The role of Responsible
OL,9,FOfficer requires that they investigate
OL,10,Flegitimate complaints made against
OL,11,Fdoctors.
OL,13,F"This is often complex and challenging
OL,14,Fand I am certain that Dr Rabey always
OL,15,Fhas the safety of patients and the
OL,16,Fpublic at the forefront of his mind
OL,17,Fwhen doing so.
