OL,3,C'It's been hell': Doctor wins legal
OL,4,Cbattle over 'flawed' work report
OL,6,F"Going forward we need to have a
OL,7,Fcloser eye on the process and make
OL,8,Fsure our clinical or specialist leads
OL,9,Fhave the right and early support to
OL,10,Fnavigate these formal processes."
OL,12,FAs part of the application for
OL,13,Fjudicial review, Conseiller Frank
OL,14,FMakepeace and Sarah Vivienne Beaumont
OL,15,Fraised concerns about the conduct of
OL,16,Fthe Sark Medical Committee and the
OL,17,Ffairness of the investigation.
