OL,3,C'It's been hell': Doctor wins legal
OL,4,Cbattle over 'flawed' work report
OL,6,FIn an interview with ITV News
OL,7,Ffollowing the review, Conseiller
OL,8,FMakepeace said of Dr Borchardt: "I
OL,9,Fthink she's been treated appallingly
OL,10,Fover the time.
OL,12,F"So many so-called experts have been
OL,13,Fin the background but don't have the
OL,14,Frelevant experience to make judgements
OL,15,Fon her career, but I believe they
OL,16,Fsought to, in a way, intimidate her
OL,17,Finto resigning."
